Title: Dream comes true
DateModified: '2019-03-04'
DatePublished: '2019-03-04'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/dream-comes-true
SetInCountry: India
Category: I didn't expect to find
AuthorName: Deepawali Parshad
AuthorCountry: India
Text: Once a time....a little child dreaming about a unique watch and he is try to
  get the watch.And this watch is his new classmate.They don't know each other.He
  is suddenly look at the watch that were his new classmate.He is try to get the watch
  .He is find everywhere but he didn't  find it.After few days he told his friend
  about his watch.His friend said that I get this watch out of our city.His friend
  never told the truth about watch.but his new friend sad every time.He  frustrated
  with his new friend because he  never tell him to where he was get this watch.He
  is study with his new friend along two years and after they meet again in college.
  Once a time he is going out of our city and enter another place.There was some shops.He
  is going in shops and seeing some gifts for his family.Suddenly his eye see the
  watch that he wants to get.And he surprised and said I didn't expect to find it.A
  clock ringing there and a voice he hear wake up son wake up. And he waked up. He
  didn't expect that was his dream. After some time his dream come true and everything
  hepen with him that he was saw in his dream.still he didn't expect to find these
  watch.
